 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92abbbb413d1d4db22efaf32bab0704f71fd8482","tid":692439,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0b6bfb11e8ad05d598226f0b573f5b50b300d4","tid":692439,"uid":107941,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b38f062cb32b837fba8045d91c775030f1cc0393","tid":692439,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T01:09:41.000Z","msg":"涂謹申不如叫支那地獄鬼國割讓廣東省比香港啦！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 民主黨係讚成發展大灣區"},{"pid":"a68da0a7c42458ec186d393812ed12f9e9106aef","tid":692439,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:19:46.000Z","msg":"早晚香港成為支那鬼國一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad82c268bd4ed96bcf2483e5a59fb399532b910","tid":692439,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4605574f715532145646669cb24d5e1f9fe2c232","tid":692439,"uid":107941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:55:05.000Z","msg":"涂謹申講一地兩檢方案徹底過唐唐<br />\n<br />\n政壇高人話，民主黨議員涂謹申今早在港台提出的幾個方法，更加徹底，他講到三個方案:<br />\n1、割地，在香港劃出屬於內地作海關檢查的土地。<br />\n<br />\n2. 授權執法，香港劃出土地讓內地執法人員在香港土地上執法檢查。<br />\n<br />\n3. 聘用內地執法人員作香港的顧問，由那些「內地顧問」作檢查，例如他們發現有人帶違禁雜誌入內地，會作出勸喻，告訴他們這些東西在內地違法。<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申亦提到香港港口碼頭海關有美國海關人員在檢查香港出口美國貨物，有先例可援。<br />\n<br />\n高人話，只要大家不把問題政治化，靈活處理，一地兩檢問題就可以解決。"},{"pid":"03dd8ed3b8cd4cecbacd7cc92cf65b768c6d25b9","tid":692439,"uid":107941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T08:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ebd72c80d9c065d71ce176f89914af056d08cc","tid":692439,"uid":107941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0241463e55281f8e8e11eb84fc1a91615dd908","tid":692439,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"香港民主黨賣港力度遠超民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d2bce60747c50c4220a1191599b6b5201ecf75","tid":692439,"uid":100697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T15:01:24.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"e5620aaaa0fc746580337ff4de69c0021e08719c","tid":692439,"uid":107941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e0241463e55281f8e8e11eb84fc1a91615dd908","tid":692439,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"香港民主黨賣港力度遠超民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地係lesser evil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c316c5554077298eadcb4d60fb948ae52cd2e701","tid":692439,"uid":107941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T03:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f96d06419a08efb6c5cc08b2e0955985943b33","tid":692439,"uid":107941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d806c026376ffd20afa625eccbc6a32790233864","tid":692439,"uid":107941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T05:28:10.000Z","msg":"民主黨就快成功爭取割地兩檢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8255aebdf6874ce805e24003d2ae7139ef77ac84","tid":692439,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T05:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c92cdd94df49a835e73cc2ca79a9a0c5257ca6","tid":692439,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T05:38:23.000Z","msg":"唔怪得港共話係順應民意<br />\n投民主黨死全家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}